name: Celltronix
body:
Celltronix is a cellular automata that can simulate some electronic stuff by drawing PNP/NPN gate in a grid. This is inspired from the flash game [Kohctpyktop](http://www.zachtronicsindustries.com/play-kohctpyktop/).

This is very early release, only the editor is working (and need a huge amount of improvement !), and no simulation can run yet.

Written with Mono using Gtk# and Cairo.
